<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 shén de líng shì xuān jiào de líng, yé sū shì xuān jiào de zhǔ.
 zài zhè gè xuān jiào de dà shí dài lǐ, wǒ men rú cǐ méng fú.
 sī chóu zhī lù yǐ jīng fā guāng, fú yīn yǐ chuān yuè yì bāng de wéi qiáng.
 zuì gāo de shān mài yǐ jià qǐ fú yīn qiáo liáng, fú yīn yào chuán biàn wàn guó wàn bāng.
 wǒ men yán zhe zhè tiáo lù qián wǎng, shǐ mìng zài jiān wǒ men yī qǐ lái káng.
 zhǔ bì qīn zì wán chéng tā de gōng, zài wǒ men zhè yī dài shēn shàng.</lyrics>
<title>xuān jiào zhī gē 迦南1124</title>
<hymn_number>1124</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>